== 遗产 ==
犹太节日[[光明节|光明节]]是为了庆祝马加比起义获胜后，洁净圣殿，重新恢复圣殿祭祀。根据犹太教拉比传统，马加比起义军只找到一个小罐的密封洁净[[橄榄油|橄榄油]]，虽然它只够圣殿里[[猶太教燈臺|犹太烛台]]燃烧一天，但却奇迹般地持续了八天，一直等到取得新压榨的油。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/Talmud/shabbat2.html |title=''Talmud'', Tractate Shabbat |accessdate=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2016-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022070631/http://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/Talmud/shabbat2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 这一神迹的真实性自中世纪以来就受到质疑。<ref>{{cite book|title=Encyclopaedia Judaica, Volume 9|last=Skolnik, Berenbaum,|first=Fred, Michael|publisher=Granite Hill Publishers, pg 332|year=2007}}</ref>

